1. *Prst* joj je bio otečen. (Her finger was swollen.)
2. On je uspeo da prstom poklopi oko. (He managed to encircle it with his finger.)
3. Prstima je zamotavao kosu. (He was braiding her hair with his fingers.)
4. Čovek je bio zbunjen i zavrtao je prstom po glavi. (The man was bewildered and he was scratching his head with his finger.)
5. Ona je prstima učarala melodiju. (She was playing a melody with her fingers.)